                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5946" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0434</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8673 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">油价寒冬中该如何生存：A油服公司人力资源规划</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to Survive in the Low Oil Price: Human Resource Planning of A Oilfield Service Corporation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙梅，吴涛，崔力文，刘莉莉，刘思怡，廖妍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中石化石油工程技术服务股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石油工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">低油价；人力资源规划；人力资源需求预测；人力资源供给预测；人力资源供需平衡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Low oil prices; Human resource planning; Human resource demand forecast; Human resource supply forecast; Human resource supply and demand balance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全球经济低迷，新冠疫情雪上加霜，国际原油价格瞬时跌入负值，石油巨头压减投资，油服公司经营形势每况愈下、人员供需失衡，纷纷断臂求生。A油服公司是专业化重组的国有石油工程技术服务公司，在高油价的年头为了抢占市场份额，招聘了大量员工并购置了重资产装备，亦在此时陷入困境。本案例描述了在这样的大背景下，国有企业A油服公司通过对当前形势和影响人力资源供需的因素进行分析，寻求人力资源供需平衡方法和措施，进而制定适合自身的人力资源战略规划，同时又为未来油价回暖的可能做好了准备。通过使用本案例，让学生了解油服公司战略调整，聚焦人力资源规划，将人力资源规划和供需平衡的理论与企业实践相结合，并思考如何应用大数据分析测算对公司的经营策略提出建设性建议。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The global economy downturns, while Corona Virus Disease 2019 adds to the depression, the price of international crude oil fell to negative, hence the major oil corporations reduce investment, then the operating situation of the oil service company is deteriorating and the supply and demand of human resource are out of balance, and they have broken their arms to survive. A Oil Service Corporation is a specialized and reorganized state-owned petroleum engineering technology service company. In the years of high oil prices, in order to seize market share, it recruited a large number of employees and purchased heavy assets and equipment, and was also in trouble at this time. In this context, the state-owned enterprise A Oil Service Corporation analyzes the current predicament and factors affecting the supply and demand of human resources, seeks methods and measures to balance the supply and demand of human resources, and then formulates suitable human resources strategic plans, and at the same time, is ready for the possibility of future oil prices. Through the use of this case, students are allowed to understand the strategic adjustment of the oil service company, focus on human resource planning, combine the theory of human resource planning and the balance of supply and demand with corporate practice, and think about how to apply big data analysis and calculation to propose constructive business strategies for the company.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源战略规划</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
